#Text=Look Fabulous All the Time
#Text=Hey , have you ever wished you could look fabulous all the time ?
#Text=Whatever you 're doing , going to school , going to work , on a date , out shopping , hitting the beach or hitting the gym - You can be constantly fabulous !
#Text=Just read this guide .
#Text=Steps
#Text=Be confident !
#Text=Stand tall and smile , or all of your hard work will go to waste .
#Text=Never stand in a corner or try to avoid attention or no one will notice how fabulous you look .
#Text=Have a clear face .
#Text=Use a product like Proactive if you have zits .
#Text=Make sure to wash your face daily , and that you are free of acne before attempting the next step , or you could cause a break-out .
#Text=Wash as often as you need , daily showers are the norm .
#Text=No one will care how fabulous you look if you smell like sweat !
#Text=Carry around a little make up pouch with you with your favorite products .
#Text=In your make up pouch , you should have at least your eyeliner , blush , lip gloss and mascara .
#Text=A comb or hairbrush helps too .
#Text=Also keep some deodorant and chapstick just in case .
#Text=Tie up your hair into a nice , cute ponytail or smooth it out before you step out of your house .
#Text=Change your hairstyle every once in a while .
#Text=Having the same hairstyle for the whole year can become a little dull and boring .
#Text=Try a bun or braid to jazz things up .
#Text=You can even go to the stylist and ask for a snip .
#Text=Do n't leave home without checking yourself in a mirror .
#Text=Check the mirror every few hours - you could just use your make-up mirror .
#Text=Do n't try this during class , or you could get into trouble .
#Text=Carry a big bag to put all of your essentials in .
#Text=It 's easier to carry just one bag , except for your make up pouch , which can be put into your big bag , and it looks more stylish , too .
#Text=If you do not need to wear a uniform , you do n't need to wear the same outfits to school .
#Text=Look at making a capsule wardrobe - a few pieces that can mix and match to many different outfits .
#Text=Try accessories .
#Text=Something simple like earrings , bangles , or a belt can change up a look from good to fabulous .
#Text=Be true to yourself and your own style .
#Text=Do n't listen too much to other people 's advice especially if it does n't sound like it will work .
#Text=Get a good night 's sleep every night .
#Text=This way you 'll look fresh in the morning .
#Text=Sleep also will reduce dark spots under the eyes .
#Text=Smell nice .
#Text=Shower in the morning and at night and wear perfume that you think smells great .
#Text=Tips
#Text=Do n't forget to smile .
#Text=It makes you feel fabulous , even on bad days .
#Text=Make sure your hair and skin are n't oily .
#Text=Try not to put hair gel as when it dries up , it looks like hair lice !
#Text=Do n't use foundation ; this causes break outs which is what you really want to avoid .
#Text=Warnings
#Text=Always be yourself .
#Text=Do not change yourself for others .
#Text=Things You 'll Need
#Text=At least 14 sets of good clothes
#Text=Makeup
#Text=Proper bags
